The paper deals with the Private Information Retrieval (PIR) problem, which is a topic in information theory and cryptography (cs.IT, cs.CR). It also establishes a relationship between PIR schemes and Locally Recoverable Codes (LRC), which are a class of storage codes (cs.DS, cs.CC, cs.DB). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
